Class Element<E>

  • java.lang.Object
    • edu.uncc.cs.bridges_vs1.structure.Element<E>
  • Type Parameters:
    E -
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    ArrayElement, DLelement, SLelement, TreeElement

    public class Element<E>
extends java.lang.Object
    This is the Superclass Element with SLelement, DLelement, ArrayElement, TreeElement, subclasses it contains the Element Visualizer object label field derived from the E value an object of E data type: integer, string, Tweet, Actor, Movie, EarthquakeTweet identifier field automatically generataed
